Nere gives the corpse one last kick and then leads you through the tunnel. Nere throws open a door, and you file into a cavernous hall, filled with ancient ruins and the wreckage of a broken bridge. In the distance, you can see the entrance to the Temple of Shar.

synopsis.value: After fighting and killing a group of duergar servants that mutinied against him, Nere takes his rage and frustration out on one of their bodies by kicking it. Once he's done, he takes the players to a nearby broken bridge and explains that he needs reinforcements. The player can promise they'll inform his boss - Chosen Ketheric - or not.
